        "action": "Remove the enforced driving ban for epilieptics on the grounds that it is unfair",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Every time an epileptic has a seizure we have to surrender our driving licence for 12 months, there is no medical evidence to suggest a second seizure in that time. Drivers with convictions can escape bans through loopholes, this seems unfair. I would like to challenge this outdated system.",
